'''Et tu, Dinobrute?''' is an [[Achievement]] in the category ''[[Wonders of the World]]''. To complete this achievement, the player needs to ignite the Flamegranate before the [[Gluttonous Yumkasaur Mountain King]] swallows it, causing the fruit to explode after being swallowed.

==Trivia==
* The achievement is a reference to the infamous line <i>{{w|et tu, Brute?}}</i> in {{w|William Shakespeare}}'s play {{w|Julius Caesar (play)|Julius Caesar}}. Caesar, in the process of being assassinated, speaks the line upon recognising his friend Brutus as one of the assassins.
